          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780525475460" href="/book/show/2232822.A_Universal_History_of_Infamy">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/54028842-kiarash?shelf=short-story-collections">short-story-collections</a>, 
