          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780525475460" href="/book/show/2232822.A_Universal_History_of_Infamy">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1895570-jim?shelf=borges">borges</a>, 
